name: Rin Hoshizora - Love Live!
description:
Hi, one information if you need, she original eye color is light green, but AI don't have this, and my training dataset is with cards of allstars set, and here she eyes color is more like yellow.

Weight is your choice, but i like 0.45 ~ 0.5

Tags you'll need: 1girl, solo, hoshizora rin, orange hair, yellow eyes, short hair,

this tags you can change or add example: green eyes, flat chest or small breasts.

If you like my LoRAs, please support me on ko-fi

Follow me on pixiv

Please comment what you want to see next (main characters of lovelive! )
